OL,3,CFootage shows first Live Facial
OL,4,CRecognition arrest
OL,6,FTwo people have been charged with
OL,7,Fcourt offences following the use of
OL,8,FLive Facial Recognition in Bolton.
OL,10,FThe arrests, made on Thursday 30
OL,11,FOctober, were the first by Greater
OL,12,FManchester Police (GMP) to use the
OL,13,Fsoftware, which was rolled out earlier
OL,14,Fin October.
OL,16,FLewis Moss, 32, from Preston, has been
OL,17,Fcharged with breach of court bail
OL,18,Fconditions in relation to domestic
OL,19,Fviolence offences.
