OL,6,FIsabelle Bateman-Bogart, 19, from
OL,7,FBolton, has been charged with breach
OL,8,Fof a court order.
OL,10,FInspector Jon Middleton from GMP's
OL,11,FLive Facial Recognition Unit said:
OL,12,F"This technology allows us to be more
OL,13,Fproactive in identifying and locating
OL,14,Findividuals who are wanted or missing,
OL,15,Fwhile also ensuring that our officers
OL,16,Fcan respond swiftly and appropriately.
