OL,6,F"Deployments like this one in Bolton
OL,7,Fshows how facial recognition can
OL,8,Fsupport in policing, whilst providing
OL,9,Fan active presence in the community to
OL,10,Fensure trust and confidence in the
OL,11,FForce."
OL,13,FGreater Manchester was chosen as the
OL,14,Fhub for two specialist vans to be
OL,15,Fdeployed in crime hotspots across the
OL,16,Fnorth west or when major events take
OL,17,Fplace.
OL,19,FThe cameras focus on faces in a crowd
OL,20,For busy streets, to help identify
OL,21,Fthose on "police watch lists".
